<item>
            <title>[KAFKA-592] Register metrics beans at kafka server startup </title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-592</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;jmx beans are not registered until the corresponding part of the code executes. To set alerts on some of the server side beans, they need to be registered at server startup.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
