                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="13486520" author="swapnilghike" created="Mon, 29 Oct 2012 23:51:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Change made to register AllTopicsProduceFailurePerSec, AllTopicsFetchFailurePerSec, OfflinePartitionsPerSec and UncleanLeaderElectionsPerSec in server.startup()&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;UnderReplicatedPartitionCount is already registered in startup with the creation of replicaManager. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;BrokerTopicStat.getBrokerAllTopicStat() also registers three other beans - AllTopicsMessagesInPerSec, AllTopicsBytesInPerSec and AllTopicBytesOutPerSec. But that&apos;s probably ok since these beans would be created anyways in most cases.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13486594" author="junrao" created="Tue, 30 Oct 2012 01:37:50 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for the patch. +1. Committed to 0.8 by making registerStats private and adding a comment.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
